微流體力學原理及應用                     MICROHYDRODYNAMICS: THEORY AND APPLICATIONS


1.Vector/tensor calculus in Einstein notation2.Equation of motion and continuity equation3.Linearity and fundamental solutions of Stokes flow4.Lorentz’s reciprocal theorem and Faxen’s law5.Boundary integral representation6.Slender body theory and applications7.Hydrodynamic interactions8.Phoretic swimming9.Electrokinetic transport10.Microrheology11.Colloidal suspensions12.Dynamics of single molecule polymer

課程教育目標 

A 厚植專業知識與應用能力 Enhance professional knowledge and application skill/abilityB 強化獨立思考及創新研發能力 Strengthen independent thinking and innovative research and development 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

A 專精之化工知識及開發前瞻技術之能力。

B 獨立思考、規劃與執行研究計畫、撰寫研究報告及口頭發表之能力。

C 結合理論知識與實務操作以解決工程問題之能力。

D 結合化工專業知識與跨領域技術以發展新興科技之能力。


